
Overview of noun unification

The noun unification has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                    
1. (1) fusion, merger, unification -- (an occurrence that involves the production of a union)
2. union, unification -- (the state of being joined or united or linked; "there is strength in union")
3. union, unification, uniting, conjugation, jointure -- (the act of making or becoming a single unit; "the union of opposing factions"; "he looked forward to the unification of his family for the holidays")
